room_title: Escape room "Down The Rabbit Hole" by Amazing Escape Room Bloomfield in New York
room_description: You knew better than to chase that rabbit! When it darted around a tree with you right on it’s heels it darted down a hole, following as fast as you can you dove in. Something was strange though, this was no normal rabbit hole, when you finally reached the bottom there was no rabbit to be found and even worse, you’re stuck.
